    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic work to become reliable. The engine currently runs roughly and has several active fluid leaks that need immediate attention. The exterior shows significant wear with rust spots and faded paint, while the interior requires a deep clean and some upholstery repair. It is a project car for someone willing to invest time and resources into its restoration.",
